================================================================================

   A collection of procedures from CMLIB (The NIST Core Math Library, https://www.nist.gov/itl/math/software)

================================================================================

   DTENSBS (September 2019)

   Interpolation of two and three dimensional gridded data using tensor products
   of one dimensional B-spline basis functions. The original
   sources for DB2VAL and DB3VAL are modified in order to accept user provided
   parameters ILOY, ILOZ, INBVX for efficient processing.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   FFTPKG (January 2024)

   A package of procedures which perform Fast Fourier Transforms for both
   complex and real periodic sequences.
   IMPLICIT DOUBLE PRECISION (A-H, O-Z)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   QUADPKD (February 2024)

   A package of procedures for computing definite integrals of various forms.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


